      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOW AWESOME (2) flew the lids from the middle with a sensational turn of foot before finishing third (20.42) and beaten 5.5 lengths over 350m at Traralgon. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in six starts. Sure to be about the mark. POETIC STAR (6) finished in the minors last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 400m at Warragul, taking a Grade 5 in a handy 22.75. Top win two back and can measure up again. SCOTT CHARISMA (8) has missed the frame at her last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when second (22.25) at this track in a Grade 4/5. Expected to do much better this time. LEAP OF FAITH (1) has strong credentials at this circuit over this journey.",
